title: Vietnam advance to next round of AFC U - 20 Women Asian Cup
body_text:
HANOI, March 12 (Vietnam News/ANN): Vietnam advanced to the next qualification round of the AFC U-20 Women's Asian Cup after a 1-1 draw with India in Group F on March 11 at Pho Tho Stadium.
Both teams are level on seven points but Vietnam top the group due to their better goal difference.
